query:
SELECT id, name, 
  IF(nearbyDiveSites IS NULL OR nearbyDiveSites = '', 'EMPTY', 'HAS DATA') as dive_status,
  IF(nearbySurfSpots IS NULL OR nearbySurfSpots = '', 'EMPTY', 'HAS DATA') as surf_status
FROM island_guides 
WHERE nearbyDiveSites IS NOT NULL AND nearbyDiveSites != ''
LIMIT 5;
